textAfterTable: Closed areas Taking of Abalone is prohibited in all: aquatic reserves intertidal reef areas. Handling Abalone The diver must: carry a suitable measuring device measure abalone as soon as it has been removed from the surface it was attached to returned immediately if it is undersized bring the abalone above the high water mark before removing the meat.   Australian Herring - Tommy Ruff Minimum legal length: No minimum legal length required. Personal daily bag limit: 60 Daily boat limit 180 Similarities with juvenile Salmon Tommy Ruff look very similar to juvenile Salmon. Make sure you know the difference to make sure undersize Salmon are returned to the water.
